trans-unit.source: Attribute that contains information about a Workflow markup file.
trans-unit.target: 包含工作流程標記檔案的相關資訊的屬性。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowMarkupSourceAttribute"></xref> class, initializing the values of <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowMarkupSourceAttribute.FileName*> and <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowMarkupSourceAttribute.MD5Digest*>.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowMarkupSourceAttribute"></xref>類別，初始化的值<> *> 和<> *>。

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the file name of the mark up file.
trans-unit.target: 包含標記檔案的檔案名稱的字串。

trans-unit.source: A string representing the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowMarkupSourceAttribute.MD5Digest*>for the file.
Gets the name of the file represented by this instance.
trans-unit.target: 取得這個執行個體所表示之檔案的名稱。

trans-unit.source: The name of the file represented by this instance
trans-unit.target: 這個執行個體所表示的檔案名稱

trans-unit.source: Gets the MD5 hash algorithm computed checksum that is associated with the workflow markup source file.
trans-unit.target: 取得 MD5 雜湊演算法計算總和檢查碼與工作流程標記的來源檔案相關聯。

trans-unit.source: This value is used to compare if the workflow markup file has been changed.
trans-unit.target: 這個值用來比較如果工作流程標記檔案已變更。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the checksum associated with the workflow markup source file.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.String>，其中包含與工作流程標記的來源檔案相關聯的總和檢查碼。</xref:System.String>
